safenet.jcprov.constants
Class KDF

java.lang.Object
  safenet.jcprov.constants.KDF

public class KDF
extends java.lang.Object

Class defining Cprov CKD_...KDF constants - ECDH Key Derive Function constants.

Further information concerning the various Key Derive Function values is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
